collectionMetadata.name: Basic Wage Change
collectionMetadata.description: Data are collected from the Survey on Annual Wage Changes. The survey covers private sector establishments with at least 10 employees. The data collected pertain to full-time resident employees in continuous employment of at least one year.

datasetMetadata.name: Basic Wage Change By Industry
datasetMetadata.description: Basic Wages refers to the basic pay before deduction of employee CPF contributions and personal income tax. It excludes employer CPF contributions, bonuses, overtime payments, commissions, allowances.
